Jordanian side the development of situations in the region,
particularly the Israeli-Palestinian talks.
</P>
<P>
Majali urged Israel to carry out the signed agreements,
particularly those regarding Israel's troop pullback in the West
Bank, in a bid to start the final status talks as soon as possible.
</P>
<P>
