the market consolidated recent record gains, with the DAX-30 index
51.60 points lower at 4,536.83.
</P>
<P>
In Paris, the CAC-40 index suffered the biggest losses, down
61.3 points or 1.89 percent at 3,178.70, by extending losses
during late trade in response to losses on the Dow Jones index.
The market had dropped during the morning session on overnight
declines in Asian markets. 
