In addition, Soffen said, Israel had prohibited officials of
the International Red Cross Committee (IRCC) and the detainees'
families from visiting the Al-Khiam Detention Center since last
December.
</P>
<P>
The Lebanese Foreign Ministry stressed in a letter to the
conference that it will continue its diplomatic contacts and
efforts to seek the release of the Lebanese detainees.
</P>
<P>
Lebanese government and IRCC officials, families of the
detainees and representatives of a number of international
agencies were present at the conference. 
