denounce the use of force in solving the Iraq-U.S. standoff.
</P>
<P>
In a statement issued after its session Thursday, the Yemeni
parliament stressed the importance of diplomatic means in dealing
with the current crisis caused by Iraq's denial of free access to
U.N. inspectors its presidential sites suspected of hiding
weapons of mass destruction.
</P>
