<HEADLINE> Xinhua World News Summary at 22:00 GMT, February 13 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI -- Vietnam became a full member of the ASEAN Promotion
Center (APC) on Thursday, Vietnam News Agency reported Friday.
</P>
<P>
