Richardson, held talks with Japanese Prime Minister Ryutaro
Hashimoto and Foreign Minister Keizo Obuchi.
</P>
<P>
"Japan and the United States shared the view that a diplomatic
solution, based on full Iraqi compliance with all relevant
U.N. Security Council resolutions, is the best solution, and that
all options remain on the table," the statement said.
(Japan-U.S.-Statement) 
