<P>
CAIRO -- The Egyptian Minister of Trade and Supply Ahmed Gweili
has disclosed that his ministry is about to complete the economic
and trade aspect of the ongoing preparations for the convocation
of a summit of the Group of 15, due to take place in Cairo early
