<HEADLINE> Results of Women's 500m Speed Skating First Run </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAGANO, Japan, February 13 (Xinhua) -- Following the results of the
women's 500-meter speed skating first run race at the Nagano Winter
Olympics on Friday:
</P>
<P>
1.Catriona Lemay-Doan, Canada, 38.39 seconds (new Games record)
</P>
<P>
2. Susan Auch, Can, 38.42
</P>
<P>
3. Tomomi Kkazaki, Jpn, 38.55
</P>
<P>
4. Koyko Shimazaki, Jpn, 38.75
</P>
<P>
5. Franziska Schenk, Can, 38.88
</P>
<P>
6. Christin Witty, Usa, 39.09
</P>
<P>
7. Svetlana Shurova, Rus, 39.11
</P>
<P>
7. Monique Garbrecht, Ger, 39.12
