Ukraine has set up 13 channels for attracting foreign investment
and has already received a total of 2.7 billion dollars in loan.
</P>
<P>
Ukraine is now negotiating with Japan, Turkey, Poland, Britain,
Denmark, Norway and Finland for special credit to boost its
exports. 
