<HEADLINE> Mexico: No Protectionist Measures Towards Asian Countries </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, February 12 (Xinhua) -- Mexican Vice Minister of
Commerce and Industrial Development Decio de Maria Serrano ruled
out the possibility of using protectionist measures in monitoring
imports from the Asian countries Thursday.
</P>
