<TEXT>
<P>
NEW YORK, February 12 (Xinhua) -- U.S. stocks remained bullish
Thursday with the Dow Jones industrial average gaining 55.05 to
close at 8,369.60, the third straight record close since Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Broader market indexes also finished higher with the Standard &AMP;
Poor's 500 stock list index rising 4.13 to 1,024.14, the New York
Stock Exchange (NYSE) composite index up 1.86 to 532.61, and the
