million shares previously, according to preliminary figures.
</P>
<P>
The Russell 2000 index of smaller companies rose 0.38 to 452.40
and the small-company dominated American Stock Exchange composite
index rose 1.82 to 686.15.
</P>
<P>
The market rebounded from a midday low when the Dow suffered a
76 point loss because of profit-taking following a gain of 134.03
in two previous sessions and Wednesday's record close of 8,314.55,
which was Dow's first close crossing the 8,300 mark. 
